OL,3,CPlaid Cymru pledges to cut tax for
OL,4,Csmall businesses
OL,6,FPlaid Cymru's Economy spokesperson has
OL,7,Fpromised to cut taxes for small,
OL,8,Findependent businesses if the party
OL,9,Fgets into power after next year's
OL,10,FSenedd election.
OL,12,FLuke Fletcher announced the plans at
OL,13,Fhis party's conference in Llandudno on
OL,14,FSaturday.
