OL,6,F"They're paying the same rate, the
OL,7,Fbusiness rates at the moment, as Costa
OL,8,Fjust around the corner.
OL,10,F"So that's not a fair system. So the
OL,11,Fbeauty of this is actually it's not
OL,12,Fgoing to cost anything.
OL,14,F"We're just rejigging it and making
OL,15,Fsure that the balance is right."
