OL,3,CPlaid Cymru pledges to cut tax for
OL,4,Csmall businesses
OL,6,FDuring his conference speech, Luke
OL,7,FFletcher said: "Our plan will see
OL,8,Fcapital built, retained and recycling
OL,9,Fin our communities, instead of it
OL,10,Fleaking ` and in some cases flooding `
OL,11,Fout of Wales.
OL,13,F"It will grow and sustain Welsh-owned
OL,14,Fbusinesses, delivering good jobs,
OL,15,Freviving our town centres, and
OL,16,Fboosting living standards.
OL,18,F"I am clearer now than ever that Wales
OL,19,Fneeds a Government with real vision
OL,20,Fand with fire in its belly.
